description: Finished it. Definitely dragged on a bit at the end. The sword fighting also kind of peaked in the middle and got shitty again toward the end. Overall, very mediocre and boring game with some cool moments. Generally bad though, and I don't think I want to speedrun it... the only thing that makes me want to run it is the fact that no one has yet.
